Introduction
------------

libtinynotify-systemwide provides a system-wide notifications module
for [libtinynotify][1]. It is based on old [sw-notify-send][2] project.

All it does is looking over procfs (/proc) for all D-Bus session buses,
and trying to send the notification to every one of them.

[1]:https://github.com/mgorny/libtinynotify/
[2]:https://github.com/mgorny/sw-notify-send/

